snippet.title: Insectipede
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1097650/Insectipede/

Epic: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/insectipede-a2174d

Microsoft: https://apps.microsoft.com/detail/9nj4ncl24hr4

Amazon: https://www.amazon.com/LoadUpGames-com-Insectipede/dp/B07TP65B72

Google: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.loadupgames.insectipede


A New Bug Blasting Arcade Game!

We’re Bugging Out!

Blast your way through 50 Challenging Stages with Waves of Insects and UFOs, Power-Ups, and Arcade High Scores. 

FEATURES

- A Bug Blasting Arcade Game.
- 50 Challenging Stages with Vibrant Colors.
- Waves of Insects and UFOs.
- Arcade High Scores.
- Power-Ups.
- Gamepad Support.

Time To Bug Out… Are You Ready For It?
